== Sea temperature== Average annual temperature of sea is about 16&nbsp;°C. In February, the average sea temperature is 12&nbsp;°C. In August, the average sea temperature is 21&nbsp;°C. From July to September, average temperature of sea exceed 20&nbsp;°C.<ref name=weather2travel>{{cite web|url=http://www.weather2travel.com/climate-guides/spain/bilbao.php|title=Weather2Travel.com: Bilbao Climate and Weather Averages}}</ref>
