on|Wannon]] || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] |- bgcolor=#4682B4 | 23 || [[Bob Hawke]] || [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]] || [[Division of Wills|Wills]] || [[Australian Labor Party|Labor]] |- bgcolor=#E0FFFF | 24 || [[Paul Keating]] || [[New South Wales]] || [[Division of Blaxland|Blaxland]] || [[Australian Labor Party|Labor]] |- bgcolor=#E0FFFF | 25 || [[John Howard]] || [[New South Wales]] || [[Division of Bennelong|Bennelong]] || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] |- bgcolor=#CC6666 | 26 || [[Kevin Rudd]] || [[Queensland]] || [[Division of Griffith|Griffith]] || [[Australian Labor Party|Labor]] |- bgcolor=#4682B4 | 27 || [[Julia Gillard]] || [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]] || [[Division of Lalor|Lalor]] || [[Australian Labor Party|Labor]] |- bgcolor=#E0FFFF | 28 || [[Tony Abbott]] || [[New South Wales]] || [[Division of Warringah|Warringah]] || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] |- bgcolor=#E0FFFF | 29 || [[Malcolm Turnbull]] || [[New South Wales]] || [[Division of Wentworth|Wentworth]] || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] |- bgcolor=#E0FFFF | 30 || [[Scott Morrison]] || [[New South Wales]] || [[Division of Cook|Cook]] || [[Liberal Party of Australia|Liberal]] |}
